verbose_text: Based on the alignment of regRNP17 with snord94, we predicted that the interaction of regRNP17 with snord94 would disrupt the interaction of snord94 with U6 snRNA (denoted by faint bands between snord94 and U6 snRNA in XREF_FIG A).
evidence: regRNP17 with snord94 would disrupt the interaction of snord94
